General.Name: Coala Life Group AB
General.Description: Coala-Life Group AB (publ), a medical device company, develops, manufactures, and sells cardiac diagnostics and mobile health products in the United States. It offers Coala Heart Monitor, a medical device and service that is used for digital remote monitoring, analysis, and self-screening of the heart; and Coala Care portal, a cloud-based solution to help healthcare professionals prescribe, manage, communicate, and diagnose patients remotely. Coala-Life Group AB (publ) was incorporated in 1994 and is based in Uppsala, Sweden.
